data.description: Welcome to this updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in Greenacres, offering comfortable one-level living on over 1/2 acre. The new kitchen and flooring bringing a fresh touch, completed by tile work in baths and kitchen. The interior boasts a cohesive look with fresh paint, while the vinyl siding enhances curb appeal. The house features a chimney, allowing the option for a wood stove. The practicality of an oversized 2-car garage and main floor utilities adds a convenience. Outside, there's room to explore with potential for a workshop or garden. Located in Central Valley Schools, it's close to Spokane Valley and Liberty Lake, making it a practical choice for easy living. Don't miss this opportunity!
